      "role": "user",
      "content": "that screwdriver thing sounds kinda weird lol. i'm more worried about the actual structure though. if i look in the attic or the basement, what specifically should i be looking for to see if the wall is part of the main support system? like what kind of beams or stuff am i looking for?",
